<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Homepage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/homeStyle.css">

    <!--to add font style -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!--to add css style -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@6.1.1/css/fontawesome.min.css" integrity="sha384-zIaWifL2YFF1qaDiAo0JFgsmasocJ/rqu7LKYH8CoBEXqGbb9eO+Xi3s6fQhgFWM" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <!--to add bootstrap icons-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.8.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css" integrity="sha384-eoTu3+HydHRBIjnCVwsFyCpUDZHZSFKEJD0mc3ZqSBSb6YhZzRHeiomAUWCstIWo" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>
<body>
    <section class="header">
        <nav>
            <a href="/home"><img src="/css/logo.jpg" class="logo"alt="logo"></a>
            <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
                <!--to add cross closing icon-->
                <i class="bi bi-x" onclick="hideMenu()"></i>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/aboutUs">ABOUT</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/menu">MENU</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">CONTACT</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/cart">CART</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/logout">LOGOUT</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <i class="bi bi-list" onclick="showMenu()"></i>
        </nav>
        <div class="text-box">
            <h1>Hello {{name}}<br>Welcome to Richard's Cakes</h1>
            <p>Bored of having cream cakes? Try out our various wine, rum and plain cakes.<br>
            Enhancing your love for cakes.. Feel the richness...!</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="hero-btn">Contact us to know more</a>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!--Menu-->
    <section class="menu">
        <h1>Menu We Offer</h1>
        <p>Our motto is to provide you with the most authentic and appetizing tastes through our cakes!</p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="menu-col-1">
                <h3>Wine Cakes</h3>
                <p>We provide five flavours in this category. 
                    The fruits used are firstly hand picked from the 
                    market, sun dried to prevent them from spoiling while
                    being stored.These fruits are then dipped in an authentic 
                    Wine over a period of time to absorb the final taste we serve..</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-col-2">
                <h3>Plain Cakes</h3>
                <p>These are non-alcoholic cakes. The fruits used are firstly hand picked from the 
                    market, sun dried to prevent them from spoiling while
                    being stored. A secret recipe is performed on these fruits 
                    which makes the cake juicy and spongy..</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-col-3">
                <h3>Rum Cakes</h3>
                <p>We provide five flavours in this category. 
                    The fruits used are firstly hand picked from the 
                    market, sun dried to prevent them from spoiling while
                    being stored.These fruits are then dipped in a clear Rum
                    over a period of time to absorb the final taste we serve..</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!--orders-->
    <section class="orders">
        <h1>Our Most Loved Orders</h1>
        <p>Based On Our Customer Reviews</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="order-col">
                <img src="/css/pic1.jpg">
                <div class="layer">
                    <h3>BlueBerry Rum Cake</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="order-col">
                <img src="/css/pic2.jpg">
                <div class="layer">
                    <h3>Cranberry Wine Cake</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="order-col">
                <img src="/css/pic4.jpg">
                <div class="layer">
                    <h3>Plum Rum Cake</h3>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

    <!--Item description-->
    <section class="desc">
        <h1>Order Description</h1>
        <p>This is a brief description of few of our cakes.</p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="desc-col">
                <img src="/css/Bg1.jpg">
                <h3>Cranberry Wine Cake</h3>
                <p>Sun dried cranberry's dipped in most authentic Wine.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="desc-col">
                <img src="/css/ChocoWalnutCake.jpeg">
                <h3>Choco-Walnut Cake</h3>
                <p>Non-alcoholic cake, with the goodness of Walnuts and milk chocolate.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="desc-col">
                <img src="/css/image4.jpeg">
                <h3>Blueberry Rum Cake</h3>
                <p>Luscious blueberry's dipped in strong Rum flavour.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!--testimonials-->
    <section class="testimonial">
        <h1>Customer Reviews</h1>
        <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="test-col">
                <div class="review">
                    <p>Ordered a cherry wine cake through this website.
                        Thought that they were going to use artificial cherries, 
                        but turned out, they are true to their words. 
                        Thankyou Richards cake for delivering the cake on time.
                        The cake was delicious.</p>
                    <h3>Bhavesh Khandelwal</h3>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="test-col">
                <div class="review">
                    <p>Tried rum plum cake for the first time.
                        The flavour was unique, quantity of fruit used was fullfilling.
                        Not like ordinary cake shops. Really a good experience.</p>
                    <h3>Shubhankar Patti</h3>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-half"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to action-->
    <section class="cta">
        <h1>Order now from our website,<br> to try our available flavours..!</h1>
        <a href="/menu" class="hero-btn">SEE MENU</a>
    </section>

    <!--Footer-->
    <section class="footer">
        <h4>ABOUT US</h4>
        <p>We guarantee the best authentic flavors, we guarantee the best spongy wine and rum cakes that 
            you will ever encounter in your life.
            We provide flavors like cranberry, blueberry, plum, mixed fruit, strawberry, cherry. 
            We also provide plain cakes, walnut cakes, choco walnut cakes, mixed fruit cakes with 
            No wine and rum (zero alcohol).</p>
            <div class="icons">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Richards-wine-cakes-rum-cakes-190578039140727/" target="_blank" ><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/richards_wine_and_rum_cakes/" target="_blank"><s class="bi bi-instagram"></s></a>
                <a href="#" target="_blank"><d class="bi bi-whatsapp"></d></a>
            </div>
    </section>
    
    <script>
        //Javascript for toggle menu
        var navLinks = document.getElementById("navLinks");
        function showMenu(){
            navLinks.style.right="0";
        }
        function hideMenu(){
            navLinks.style.right="-200px";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>